  "prompt": "What are the best baby boy names starting with BH?",
  "response": "Choosing a name for your baby boy is a special decision. Names starting with \"Bh\" can be unique and culturally significant. Here are a few suggestions:\n\n1. **Bhavesh** - A name of Indian origin meaning \"Lord of the world.\"\n2. **Bhavik** - An Indian name meaning \"devout\" or \"pure.\"\n3. **Bharat** - A name with historical significance in India, representing the nation itself or \"universal monarch.\"\n4. **Bhaskar** - Meaning \"sun\" or \"bright,\" this name has roots in Indian tradition.\n5. **Bhupen** - Meaning \"king\" in Sanskrit, representing royalty and leadership.\n\nThese names might resonate with you due to their powerful meanings and cultural backgrounds.",
